Module com.example.cab302assessment10b0101
Package com.example.cab302assessment10b0101.model

Interface BookDAOInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
MockBookDAO
public interface BookDAOInterface
The BookDAOInterface defines the contract for the data access operations related to Book objects. It is specifically used for the MockBookDAO, which imitates the behavior of BookDAO during unit testing in BookDAOTest.
